reshape long v, i(patient) j(visit)


* 2 Use meglm, not old tools:

meglm v drug male age bl || patient:, family(ordinal) intpoints(12)
estimates store meglm1

predict meglm1re, reffect
predict meglm1xb, xb
predict meglm1eta, eta
predict meglm1mu*, mu



